3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper discusses the difference between dense and sparse codes, which are relevant to social and information networks. 
4. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper talks about the computational complexity of detection, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper mentions noiseless channels, which are relevant to multimedia communication.
